  S → NT24 NT113  
  S → NT13 NT94  
  S → NT39 NT68  

The only direct terminal expansions among these nonterminals are

  NT39→'t11', NT68→'t3'  
  NT94→'t1', NT113→'t7'  

None can produce the pair ‘t2’ then ‘t12’.  Hence the grammar cannot derive “t2 t12.”
